Source: https://github.com/matthuisman/pinn-os
This is only to add Batocera Beta and Stable builds for RPI4 to PINN OS list and fixing some things that were outdated in the source

Changes:

* Fixed nominal partition size to 3GB (3096) as Batocera will not be able to update otherwise
* Fixed partition name to "BATOCERA" instead of "Recalbox"
* Changed default password to mirror Batocera's default password
* Fixed uncompressed tar.xz size value to 1602
* Fixed download size to match current version 5.26
* Added RPI4 Models support info and hex revisions to jsons
* Updated url outdated url to new batocero.org url
